{
  "title": "Flaky Polish Potato Pie",
  "description": "A savory, flaky pastry filled with creamy potato and pico de gallo sauce, perfect for a comforting dinner. Rests to ensure flakiness without overcooking.",
  "cuisine": "polish",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
